"     Edward R Yeomans, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?7/43/7858/contributors\">",
"     Clint M Cormier, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
